high_descs: Turn around and walk up to a sink table in the upper right.
Pick up a pen from the sink table.
Turn around and step forward to a desk in front of you.
Place the pen on the desk.
Go back to the sink table.
Pick up a pen from the sink table.
Move back to the desk.
Place the pen on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens on the desk.

high_descs: Turn back and walk then turn right towards the sink counter top.
Pick up the middle pen out of three pens from the sink counter top.
Turn back towards the desk.
Put the pen on the back side of the table lamp on the desk.
Turn back to the sink counter top.
Pick up the left side pen from the sink counter top.
Turn back towards the desk.
Put the second pen in front of the first pen and beside the table lamp on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens near the table lamp on the desk.

high_descs: Turn left to reach the sink counter top.
Pick up the pen on the right from the sink counter top.
Turn around to reach the desk.
Put the pen on the desk.
